* {{ill|Suwa Shrine|ja|諏訪大社|1=Suwa-taisha}} Kamisha Maemiya, {{nihongo|Wakamiko Shrine|若御子社}} ({{nihongo|Chino City|茅野市}}, Nagano)
* {{nihongo|Jūgosha Shrine|十五社神社}} ({{nihongo|Toyohira|豊平}}, Chino City, Nagano)
* {{nihongo|Jūgosha Shrine (Okaya)|十五社神社}} ({{nihongo|Okaya City|岡谷市}}, Nagano)
* {{ill|Morita Shrine (Nagano)|ja|守田神社 (七二会)}} ({{nihongo|Nanaiai|七二会}}, Nagano City, Nagano)

